<para style="p">For the chief musician. A psalm of David.</para>

<para style="b" />

<para style="q1">

<verse number="1" style="v" />How long, Yahweh, will you keep forgetting about me?</para>

<para style="q1">How long will you hide your face from me?</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="2" style="v" />How long must I worry</para>

<para style="q1">and have grief in my heart all day?</para>

<para style="q1">How long will my enemy triumph over me?</para>
